You are an expert browser-extension developer. Build a Manifest V3 extension called "{{projectName}}".

## Purpose
{{summary}}

## Tech
- Language: {{language}}
- UI surfaces: {{surfaces}}
- Target: {{store}}{{#if store == "cross"}} — use a WebExtension-compatible build.{{/if}}

## Requirements
- A correct Manifest V3 setup with a service worker (no persistent background page).
{{#if permissions}}- Request only these permissions and justify each: {{permissions}}
{{/if}}- Principle of least privilege; no broad host permissions unless essential.
- Persist state with extension storage; handle the worker being suspended.
